OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FExam 'anti-cheating' hats  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fgo viral in Philippines    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Images of students wearing so-called   
OL,6, "anti-cheating hats" during college    
OL,7, exams have gone viral on social media  
OL,8, in the Philippines, sparking amusement.
OL,10,FStudents at one college in Legazpi City
OL,11,Fwere asked to wear headgear that would 
OL,12,Fprevent them peeking at others' papers.
OL,14,FMany responded by creating homemade    
OL,15,Fcontraptions out of cardboard, egg     
OL,16,Fboxes and other recycled materials.    
OL,18,FTheir tutor told the BBC she had been  
OL,19,Flooking for a "fun way" to ensure      
OL,20,F"integrity and honesty" in her classes.
